Holotype .
MHUA-A 12212 , adult male from Colombia , department of Antioquia , municipality of Valdivia, vereda San Fermín, “La Selva” Natural Reserve ( 7.094899 , -75.482269 ;
1850 m a.s.l.
), collected on
